{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/React.js/ComponentJsx/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"코딩코딩","author":"[Hwisung, Kim]","siteUrl":"https://gatsby-starter-bee.netlify.com","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"Heessong/blog-comments"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"jbee"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"0fce78c4-2503-573b-8fb1-a67dd0178cec","excerpt":"란 재활용 가능한 의 구성 단위이다 어떠한 UI구성요소를 만들때 로 만들면 추후에 같은 UI구성요소를 만들때 그대로 재활용하여 사용할 수 있다 는 또 다른 를 포함 할 수 있으며 단위로 분리되어있기때문에 코드의 수정 및 유지보수에도 훨씬 용이하다 Class Component(클래스형) 에서는 반드시  함수가 있어야한다 함수안에 있는 코드를 한다 Functional Component(함수형) 는 보다 훨씬 코드가 간결하며 마찬가지로 코드들을 한다 JSX (JavaScript Syntax…","html":"<p><code class=\"language-text\">Component</code>란 재활용 가능한 <code class=\"language-text\">UI</code>의 구성 단위이다</p>\n<p>어떠한 UI구성요소를 만들때 <code class=\"language-text\">Component</code>로 만들면 추후에 같은 UI구성요소를 만들때 그대로 재활용하여 사용할 수 있다</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Component</code>는 또 다른 <code class=\"language-text\">Component</code>를 포함 할 수 있으며 <code class=\"language-text\">UI</code>단위로 분리되어있기때문에 코드의 수정 및 유지보수에도 훨씬 용이하다</p>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"class-component클래스형\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#class-component%ED%81%B4%EB%9E%98%EC%8A%A4%ED%98%95\" aria-label=\"class component클래스형 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Class Component(클래스형)</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//react 패키지를 받아오는것</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Component</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">React<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Component</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//컴포넌트명 선언</span>\n\t<span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>클래스형 컴포넌트<span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> Component <span class=\"token comment\">//다른 컴포넌트에서 재사용 할수 있게 export</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Class Component</code>에서는 반드시 <code class=\"language-text\">render</code> 함수가 있어야한다</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">render</code>함수안에 있는 <code class=\"language-text\">JSX</code>코드를 <code class=\"language-text\">return</code>한다</p>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"functional-component함수형\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#functional-component%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98%ED%98%95\" aria-label=\"functional component함수형 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Functional Component(함수형)</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Component</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>함수형 컴포넌트<span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>h1<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n\t<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> Component</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Functional Component</code>는 <code class=\"language-text\">Class Component</code>보다 훨씬 코드가 간결하며 마찬가지로 <code class=\"language-text\">JSX</code>코드들을 <code class=\"language-text\">return</code>한다</p>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"jsx-javascript-syntax-extension\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#jsx-javascript-syntax-extension\" aria-label=\"jsx javascript syntax extension permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>JSX (JavaScript Syntax Extension)</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">JSX</code>란 <code class=\"language-text\">React</code>에서 사용하는 <code class=\"language-text\">JavaScript</code> 확장 문법이며  <code class=\"language-text\">Browser</code>에서 동작하는 과정에서 <code class=\"language-text\">Babel</code>을 사용하여 일반 <code class=\"language-text\">JavaScript</code>의 코드로 변환된다</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">HTML tag</code>를 그대로 사용할 수 있어 편리하며 또한 <code class=\"language-text\">JavaScript</code>도 동시에 사용 할 수 있다</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>사용법</p>\n<ul>\n<li>{ …JavaScript 코드 }</li>\n<li>class를 선언할때 class가 아닌 className 사용</li>\n<li>Inline Styling할때 &#x3C;div style={{color : “red”}}>Hello React</div></li>\n<li>Slef Closing tag 필수!! <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;br /&gt;</code> ,<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;input /&gt;</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;button /&gt;</code> 등등</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">JSX</code>는 내부요소들을 감싸는 최상위 요소가 있어야하는데 <code class=\"language-text\">Fragments</code>는 <code class=\"language-text\">DOM</code>에 별도의 노드를 추가하지않고 하나의 <code class=\"language-text\">Component</code>안에 여러 요소들을 그룹화 할 수 있어서 불필요한 <code class=\"language-text\">div tag</code>의 생성을 막을수 있어 유용하다</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token comment\">//Fragments</span>\n\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div className <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"LoginBtn\"</span> onclick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">=></span>console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"click\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>This is Login Button<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span> \n\t<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>br <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>  <span class=\"token comment\">//Closing tag 확실하게</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div style <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>color <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"red\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>backgroundColor <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"blue\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> width <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"100px\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>This is red<span class=\"token operator\">?</span> blue<span class=\"token operator\">?</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token comment\">//Inline Styling</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> </code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Component, JSX","date":"April 27, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/React.js/ComponentJsx/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/HTML/http/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"HTTP","category":"HTML","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/Project/WesopReview/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Wesop Review","category":"Project","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}